flowchart TD
    M[Memory<br/>content the system has seen]
    G{Evidence Gate<br/>admissibility check}
    C[Canonical Evidence<br/>may rewrite current state]
    S[Side Evidence<br/>reference only, no writes]
    P[Projection<br/>external mirror, no canonical effect]
    A[Archive<br/>historical, not current]

    M --> G
    G -->|trusted source + not expired + mission-relevant| C
    G -->|trusted but informal| S
    G -->|external projection| P
    G -->|historical, expired| A

    style C fill:#d4edda,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px
    style S fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#aaa
    style P fill:#e2e3e5,stroke:#aaa
    style A fill:#e2e3e5,stroke:#aaa
    style G fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#c0392b,stroke-width:2px
